	<p align="center"><sans_b>АЛЕКСАНДР ИВАНОВИЧ КУПРИН</sans_b></p>
	<p align="center"><sans>(1870&#8211;1938)</sans></p>
	<p align="center">
		<image_block class="top-bottom" width="300px">
